The paper focuses on face recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of 3D-aided 2D face recognition also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the robustness of the system against attacks, which relates to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the paper also discusses the security implications of the system, which falls under the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
